{"tid":2455379,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"鑒於最近全球嘅排支風氣，點解唔試吓拉幾派打一派呢？","createTime":"2021-03-21T05:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T10:16:03.000Z","uid":143131,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d21f7cf0305bd2cdc96b4addf7e24bb0c873ee39","tid":2455379,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:35:49.000Z","msg":"最近因為武漢肺炎同埋支那霸權，全球排支風氣盛行，已經有唔少非支那亞裔被外國人襲擊嘅新聞<br />\n<br />\n再加上班鬼佬根本分唔清楚亞洲人邊個國家打邊國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以一律當係支那人處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有見及此，我就係諗點解唔趁依個重大嘅機會(商機)係全球出啲商品去標明自己唔係支那人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如我哋可以出件衫叫「I&rsquo;m not Chinese I&rsquo;m HongKonger」，之後再出唔同國家嘅版本例如「I&rsquo;m not Chinese I&rsquo;m Japanese」咁樣，拉曬其他國家嘅人入自己個邊，等全球係民間上孤立支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚想見到班支那人會因應驚被人打同bully之後寧願著其他國族嘅衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376b9c85d9974efa99a4922d4a9cda8cb210d6d0","tid":2455379,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9a8d0fedf029a341e94733dec2881bddb8ae61","tid":2455379,"uid":143131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"376b9c85d9974efa99a4922d4a9cda8cb210d6d0","tid":2455379,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T07:31:24.000Z","msg":"係香港仲著乜鳩吖<br />\n依個係for身在外國嘅非支那亞洲人"},{"pid":"05476f0f6febf7d344f03470f8708e442aa12f08","tid":2455379,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:16:03.000Z","m